{"tid":1651534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議] 建地下公海  反佈防、mon post狗","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:23:14.000Z","uid":177851,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ba672cc2178ba77acfeb4c53a874edb14d424869","tid":1651534,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"重燃運動力量，越過轉捩點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有位手足提過，都好多人覺得有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大致係靠朋友拉朋友 <br />\n記住係相熟朋友，有一齊發過夢就更加好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人數不限，數量不限<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">將快閃、開花行動係tg地下公海宣傳</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其他大型民眾活動就照樣文宣 eg 遊行集會</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁平時都有小組group啦，要地下公海做咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地下公海可以保密快閃同其他行動。以往18區開花都係對外宣傳，令到啲狗仔一早佈防好曬，最重要係開花活動通常都有勇武，啲狗就更mon住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇吓佢哋今日既佈防就知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋唔洗驚俾狗同毛入黎洗走行動post ！就好似將連登行動post 集中埋係一個加左密兼冇鬼既group到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以集思廣益，理性討論！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">byebye啦mon post狗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"233bcea52e0ba56fc2a4d02694f0f9af3db61af7","tid":1651534,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb453ed36ca30c05d2514e9e85e723f6e321214","tid":1651534,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10